## Overview

A Rails 4 application showcases Binnacle.io features. It demonstrates:

- How to configure a Rails App to use Binnacle
- How to build a Real-time Feature using Binnacle Push Service
- How to use Binnacle as a Distributed Log Management Solution
- How to use Binnacle to detect errors in your Applications
- How to use Binnacle Uptime service
- How to use some of Binnacle's Ready-to-use Real-time Rails Widgets
